    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>aubergine[s]</strong> in half lengthways, then without cutting through the stalk[s], carefully slice the<strong> halved aubergine</strong> into strips, lengthways (at approx. 1cm intervals)</p><p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Drain and pat your<strong> mozzarella</strong> dry with kitchen paper (squeeze as much liquid out as you can!), then tear into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
