    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved potatoes </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Once the spiced aubergine has had 10 min, put the tray[s] in the oven for 30 min or until the potatoes are golden</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
